Start
/ GoalFirst order — call error handler first, then retry
- set %goalFirstHandled% = false
- set %goalFirstAttempts% = 0
- call AlwaysFails, on error call GoalFirstHandler, then retry 2 times
- assert %goalFirstHandled% is true, "error goal should be called in GoalFirst order"
- assert %goalFirstAttempts% is greater than 1, "AlwaysFails should be retried at least once"
